    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/bb83c70c4edaa7f8ca53f6cd84b172d5.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/bb83c70c4edaa7f8ca53f6cd84b172d5.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/bb83c70c4edaa7f8ca53f6cd84b172d5.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《The Scrap》是一款独立第三人称射击游戏，故事发生在一个由机器人居住的未来世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/5142ff35fce4c7beae68ed29b8741f5c.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/5142ff35fce4c7beae68ed29b8741f5c.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/5142ff35fce4c7beae68ed29b8741f5c.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>来见识一下B9-X，一个来自废旧堆场的机器人，他成为对抗侵略性外星人的唯一希望。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/e4e3ac40b5261c855401f031a4b45f94.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/e4e3ac40b5261c855401f031a4b45f94.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/e4e3ac40b5261c855401f031a4b45f94.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >持续战斗</h2>击败数十个危险的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/f7473f9d7ae29aed68b72e351e6ad3e5.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/f7473f9d7ae29aed68b72e351e6ad3e5.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/f7473f9d7ae29aed68b72e351e6ad3e5.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态游戏体验</h2>投身于动作，使用未来科技武器，灵活移动，并进行近身攻击。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/c3588b92c468b08c5da54152df47886c.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/c3588b92c468b08c5da54152df47886c.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/c3588b92c468b08c5da54152df47886c.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各种掩护</h2>利用掩护躲避被击中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/251111c9974f63f5990d3ae71c6bd5ac.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/251111c9974f63f5990d3ae71c6bd5ac.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/251111c9974f63f5990d3ae71c6bd5ac.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4